lines.text: I want you out! Now! Tonight! I let you live here, you're six months behind on rent and now you drive me and everyone else crazy with that damn guitar playing of yours!
Someday I'm gonna be so famous that people are gonna stand in line to hear my play!
Hey, we gotta sign that guy- I haven't seen anyone like him since uh... uh, what's his name bit that bat's head off
I'm a virgin girl. I wait 'til I'm married. I'm a virgin girl. I don't go down on my knees.
From now on, we eat OUT!
